	<div id='about-us-intro' class='avia-section main_color avia-section-default avia-no-shadow avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-0  el_before_av_section  avia-builder-el-first  four_to_two container_wrap fullsize'   ><div class='container' ><main  role="main" itemprop="mainContentOfPage"  class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-542'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
<div style='padding-bottom:14px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h1  blockquote classic-quote  avia-builder-el-1  el_before_av_hr  avia-builder-el-first   av-thin-font'><h1 class='av-special-heading-tag'  itemprop="headline"  >The <strong> Hooros Philosophy</strong></h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ></div></div></div>
<div  class='hr hr-short hr-center  avia-builder-el-2  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_one_fourth  '><span class='hr-inner ' ><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span></div>
<div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-3  el_after_av_hr  el_before_av_one_fourth  " ><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-4  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='*' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></div><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  >Who are we?</h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>Hooros is an exclusive marketplace that allows companies to work with the best, handpicked freelance talent in the African continent. </p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-5  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  " ><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-6  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='*' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></div><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  >What do we do?</h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>We assign you the best, handpicked freelance software engineers, designers and copywriters. We then proceed to manage your freelancers to ensure your project is completed on time and in accordance to your expectations.</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-7  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  " ><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-8  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='*' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></div><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  >Why do we do it?</h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>For freelancers, we want to give you a viable platform that gives them access to top freelance projects and a platform that makes freelancing a viable career option. For businesses we want to provide a risk free, cost-effective outsourcing solution</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_one_fourth  avia-builder-el-last  " ><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-10  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='*' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></div><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  >Our History</h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>Hooros was founded and launched in September 2015 initially as a landing page to test our initial idea; that talented people ultimately desire the ability to have full control of their work, who they work with and how they conduct their work and that companies are increasingly looking to work with freelancers, to reduce the number of permanent employees they need and to attract exceptional talent for particular temporary/contractual projects. We pursued a very pragmatic approach to test our assumptions, following the creed that all justifiable beliefs must be rationally justified through practical tests.</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div>

</div></div></main><!-- close content main element --></div></div><div id='about-us-team' class='avia-section alternate_color avia-section-large avia-no-shadow avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_heading  section-with-bg container_wrap fullsize'   ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-542'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
<div style='padding-bottom:10px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h6  blockquote classic-quote  avia-builder-el-12  el_before_av_heading  avia-builder-el-first  '><h6 class='av-special-heading-tag'  itemprop="headline"  >Meet Team Hooros</h6><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ></div></div></div>
<div style='padding-bottom:14px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h1  blockquote classic-quote  avia-builder-el-13  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_testimonials   av-thin-font'><h1 class='av-special-heading-tag'  itemprop="headline"  >Allow us to <strong>introduce ourselves</strong></h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ></div></div></div>
<div  data-autoplay='1'  data-interval='5'  data-animation='fade'  data-hoverpause='1'  class='avia-testimonial-wrapper avia-grid-testimonials avia-grid-2-testimonials avia_animate_when_almost_visible '>
<section class ='avia-testimonial-row'><div class='avia-testimonial av_one_half flex_column no_margin avia-testimonial-row-1 avia-first-testimonial'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><div class='avia-testimonial_inner'><div class='avia-testimonial-image'  itemprop="image" ><img width="180" height="180" src="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg" class="attachment-square size-square" alt="Emmanuel Sibanda" srcset="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg, https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg 80w, https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg 300w, https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg, https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg 120w, https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_200_200/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAlvAAAAJGM1ODRiNDM1LTgwMjAtNDkzMS1iMWNmLTMyNzc5ZDlkYThjNg.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px" /></div><div class='avia-testimonial-content '    itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><p>The Zimbabwean born Emmanuel Sibanda, is one of the Co-Founder's of Hooros and is the current CEO of Hooros (PTY) LTD. Emmanuel prides himself in having a number of skills allowing him to take an active role in everything from web development to business development and public relations. Emmanuel Sibanda is based in Cape Town<br><br><i>Emmanuel carries a LL.B, a Masters in Law and is currently pursuing a Computer Science degree part-time</i></p>
<p>Connect on: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/emmanuel-sibanda-42b49176" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></p>
</div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta'><div class='avia-testimonial-arrow-wrap'><div class='avia-arrow'></div></div><div class='avia-testimonial-meta-mini'><strong  class='avia-testimonial-name'    itemprop="name" >Emmanuel Sibanda</strong><span  class='avia-testimonial-subtitle '    itemprop="jobTitle" >Cape Town, South Africa (C.E.O)</span></div></div></div></div>
