<strong>The birth and growth of Hooros</strong></h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ></div></div></div></p>
<div  class='hr hr-short hr-center  avia-builder-el-16  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_one_third  '><span class='hr-inner ' ><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span></div>
<div class="flex_column av_one_third  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-17  el_after_av_hr  el_before_av_two_third  " ><section class='avia-team-member  avia-builder-el-18  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  team-member-kriesi'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><div class='team-img-container'><img class='avia_image avia_image_team' src='http://hooros.co.za/assets/boxify/img/hooros2.png' alt='Hooros'  itemprop="image"  /><div class='team-social'><div class='team-social-inner'><span class='hidden av_member_url_markup  twitter'  itemprop="url" >https://twitter.com/Hoorosza</span><a rel='v:url' data-avia-tooltip="Hooros on Twitter" target='_blank' class=' twitter avia-team-icon ' href='https://twitter.com/Hoorosza' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='t' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></a><span class='hidden av_member_url_markup  facebook'  itemprop="url" >https://www.facebook.com/hoorosza/</span><a rel='v:url' data-avia-tooltip="Hooros on Facebook" target='_blank' class=' facebook avia-team-icon ' href='https://www.facebook.com/hoorosza/' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='f' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></a></div></div></div><h3 class='team-member-name'   itemprop="name" >Hooros</h3><span class='hidden team-member-affiliation'  itemprop="affiliation" >Hooros - Work with the best freelance talent in Africa</span></section></div>
<div class="flex_column av_two_third  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-19  el_after_av_one_third  el_before_av_section  avia-builder-el-last  " style='border-radius:0px; '><section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><p>Choosing a different path isn't always an easy thing to do. Ultimately, success is what you make it to be, failure works the same. Your choice to be a <strong>freelancer</strong> should be an empowering one, regardless of what your mother thinks<br> You are <strong>independent</strong>, you control your work and you control your life, so why not get the respect you deserve? Untied from one employer, one office and one job<br><br><b>You are more than your job title</b><br><br>
You are hired to do a job and do it well, but what about your other skills, what about <strong>self-development</strong>? Freelancing allows you to take on more challenging work, that allows you to grow professionally and personally. Why limit yourself?<br> Our vision is to make freelancing a viable career option that simultaneously allows you to sharpen your skills.<br><br><b>Launching home-grown talent onto the world's stage.</b><br>Freelancing should be a career option with all the benefits of employment and this is exactly what we want to offer through out platform</p>

</div></section></div>
